'''Union Sportive Pont-de-Roide Vermondans''' is a [[France|French]] [[association football]] team founded in [[2003]]. They are based in [[Pont-de-Roide]], [[Franche-Comt<U+00E9>]], [[France]] and are currently playing in the [[Championnat de France Amateurs 2]] Group B, the fifth tier in the [[French football league system]]. They play at the [[Stade Municipal (Pont-de-Roide)|Stade Municipal]] in [[Pont-de-Roide]].

